      "text": "an article in \"LOOK\" Magazine, at an early date, explaining",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "the Navy's development of so-called \"flying saucers.\"",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Dr. [REDACTED] indicated he desired to refer to the FBI",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
