      "text": "of such an article would save the Bureau time and expense",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "in running down numerous reported leads regarding balloons",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "or reported saucers within the confines of this country.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "He also indicated release of erroneous information by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "amateur scientists concerning \"flying saucers\" had nearly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "caused waves of hysteria among the public in certain areas",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "of the United States. Dr. [REDACTED] explained that he had",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "submitted to the FBI Laboratory a complete explanation of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
